# Design System

Virelia uses a custom dark mode color palette:

- Primary Background: #121212 (Deep Space Black)
- Surface Background: #1E1E1E (Subtle Glow Gray)
- Primary Text: #EAEAEA (Stardust White)
- Secondary Text: #8A8A8E (Neutral Gray)
- Brand Color: #007AFF (Serenity Blue)
- Accent Color: #FF9500 (Vitality Orange)
- Success Color: #34C759 (Evergreen Green)
- Error Color: #FF3B30 (Crimson Red)

These colors should be defined as constants in a theme file and used consistently throughout the app.